high_descs: turn left and walk a bit towards the bathroom sink
pick the dirty cloth up in between the sinks
move over to the left side sink
rinse out the dirty wash cloth in the sink and pick it back up
turn around and walk over to the toilet
place the clean wash cloth on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: place a clean wash cloth on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sinks at your right.
Pick up the rag from between the sinks.
Go to the sink on the left.
Wash the rag in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the right side of the toilet.
Place the rag on the back of the toilet, on top of the other rag.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean rag on the toilet.

high_descs: Pick up the dirty purple rag from the counter.
Bring the rag to the sink on the left.
Wash the rag in the sink on the left.
Bring the rag to the toilet.
Put the rag on the toilet tank lid.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned rag on the toilet tank lid.
